primaryTopic.definition: At the University of Hull - an empowered and engaged institution - we're constantly 'going beyond' and investing in every facet of our culture in a bid to demonstrate our commitment to becoming the competitive, responsive and resilient community that will help you fulfil your potential during your time with us. Our quest for advanced knowledge has cultivated our renown for world-class, high-rated teaching, research provision, impressive facilities, and a strong support network on both Hull and Scarborough campuses. Our research, in particular, is of international acclaim in many fields, the quality of which informs our teaching at all levels.
